Document: class_@globalscope  
Path: godot/classes/class_@globalscope.rst  
Summary: Overview of global scope constants, built-in functions, and singletons accessible from anywhere in Godot, including error codes, keycodes, and property hints.  

A list of global scope enumerated constants and built-in functions. This includes all entries residing in the global scope, such as error codes, keycodes, property hints, and other commonly used values. Singletons are also documented here, as they can be accessed from anywhere in the engine. For entries specifically accessible only from GDScript, refer to @GDScript. Note: There are notable differences when using this API with C#. See doc_c_sharp_differences for more information.
---CHUNK---
