Summary: Maximum and minimum values for 8-bit, 16-bit, 32-bit, and 64-bit signed and unsigned integers.  

UINT8_MAX (unsigned 8-bit integer): Maximum value is 255.  
UINT16_MAX (unsigned 16-bit integer): Maximum value is 65535.  
UINT32_MAX (unsigned 32-bit integer): Maximum value is 4294967295.  
INT8_MIN (signed 8-bit integer): Minimum value is -128.  
INT8_MAX (signed 8-bit integer): Maximum value is 127.  
INT16_MIN (signed 16-bit integer): Minimum value is -32768.  
INT16_MAX (signed 16-bit integer): Maximum value is 32767.  
INT32_MIN (signed 32-bit integer): Minimum value is -2147483648.  
INT32_MAX (signed 32-bit integer): Maximum value is 2147483647.  
INT64_MIN (signed 64-bit integer): Minimum value is -9223372036854775808.  
INT64_MAX (signed 64-bit integer): Maximum value is 9223372036854775807.
